metadata.lyrics:
[Intro]
Twelve days to build a dream

[Verse 1]
On day one built the harness, FliGen came alive
React and Vite together, Express on the line
Day two added brains, Claude SDK arrived
Agent conversations, intelligence defined

[Verse 2]
Day three, second brain, Kybernesis in flight
Memory and context, keeping knowledge tight
Day four, images flowing, FAL and KIE unite
Pixels come to play, creating day and night

[Chorus]
Foundation's set, the journey's begun
Four days down, we're having fun
Building tools with Claude by my side
Twelve days of Claudemas, what a ride!

[Outro]
Four days done, eight more to go

metadata.name: The Creation - 12 Days of Claudemas
metadata.lyrics:
[Intro]
Creative tools come alive

[Verse 1]
Day five, voices speaking, ElevenLabs on cue
Text to speech flowing, narration coming through
Day six, videos dancing, animations breaking free
Kling and Veo rendering, motion we can see

[Verse 2]
Day seven, music playing, Suno takes the stage
Melodies and rhythms, setting up the gauge
Day eight, thumbnails shining, designs that engage
HTML and canvas, art upon the page

[Chorus]
Creating magic, bringing life to code
Four more days, we're on a roll
Building tools with vision clear
Twelve days of Claudemas, we're halfway here!

[Outro]
Eight days down, four to go
metadata.style: Indie Rock with Electronic elements, energetic and creative, 125 BPM, guitar and synths

assets.prompt: A triumphant epic cinematic rock anthem with soaring orchestral strings, powerful guitar riffs, and victorious energy

metadata.name: The Integration - 12 Days of Claudemas
metadata.lyrics:
[Intro - Building]
Bringing it all together

[Verse 1]
Day nine, connection, FliHub interop
APIs talking, data never stops
Day ten, automation, N8N workflows run
Orchestration magic, many tasks as one

[Verse 2]
Day eleven, storytelling, narratives unite
Images and voices, videos in flight
Day twelve, completion, everything's just right
Twelve tools together, shining in the light

[Chorus - Epic]
Journey's done, twelve tools complete
Claudemas magic, can't be beat
From harness to story, we built it all
Twelve days of Claudemas, hear the call!

[Bridge - Instrumental build]

[Final Chorus - Full power]
Built it with Claude, day by day
Twelve tools born, along the way
From code to creation, watched it grow
Twelve days of Claudemas, now you know!

[Outro - Triumphant]
Twelve days, one journey, mission complete
metadata.style: Epic Cinematic Rock, triumphant and powerful, 130 BPM, orchestral strings with rock guitar
